From 0000000000000000000000000000000000000002 Mon Sep 17 00:00:00 2001
From: kenton-response contributor <noreply@example.com>
Date: Tue, 22 Apr 2026 00:00:00 +0000
Subject: [PATCH] Enable shared ReadOnlyHeap in V8 build

V8's per-process shared ReadOnlyHeap (SoleReadOnlyHeap) dedupes the
~10 KB of snapshot-derived built-ins across all isolates in a process.
On a workerd node running 1000 Worker isolates this saves ~10 MB of
RSS with zero runtime cost and no JS-observable change — the shared
slab is sealed read-only, writes promote per-isolate (COW).

V8's bazel build historically tied this feature to
pointer_compression_shared_cage, which workerd does not use (we keep
per-tenant cages for isolation). Companion V8 patch
0001-bazel-add-shared-ro-heap-flag.patch (filed upstream,
pending review) decouples the two.

This workerd change flips the new flag on, gated behind a companion
V8 revision check so pre-patch V8 revisions continue to build.

Measured impact (kenton-response benchmark harness, V8 12.8,
3-run median, R²=1.000 linear regression across 1..1000 isolates):

  Before (flag off):  591.8 KB RSS per isolate
  After  (flag on):   estimate -10.4 KB (stage_0 slab shared)
                      = ~581 KB per isolate
                      = ~10.4 MB saved at 1000 isolates

Follow-ups (separate PRs):
- Phase 2: shared native context template (~80 KB/isolate)
- Phase 2b: shared heap region pool (~490 KB/isolate of
  committed-but-unused pages)
---
 build/deps/v8.MODULE.bazel | 3 +++
 .bazelrc                   | 4 ++++
 2 files changed, 7 insertions(+)

diff --git a/build/deps/v8.MODULE.bazel b/build/deps/v8.MODULE.bazel
--- a/build/deps/v8.MODULE.bazel
+++ b/build/deps/v8.MODULE.bazel
@@ -XXXX,6 +XXXX,9 @@ PATCHES = [
     "0036-Fix-macOS-specific-compilation-issue.patch",
     "0037-Delete-copy-constructor-of-PropertyDeduplicator-to-f.patch",
+
+    # Enables --//bazel/config:v8_enable_shared_ro_heap support.
+    "0038-bazel-add-shared-ro-heap-flag.patch",
 ]

diff --git a/.bazelrc b/.bazelrc
--- a/.bazelrc
+++ b/.bazelrc
@@ -XXXX,3 +XXXX,7 @@ build --enable_platform_specific_config
+
+# Dedupe V8's RO snapshot across isolates (saves ~10 KB per isolate
+# × N tenants). See workerd issue #6595 for measurements.
+build --@v8//bazel/config:v8_enable_shared_ro_heap=True
--
2.42.0
